Description.NEUTRAL: A twist on Minecraft's 1st Birthday Skin Pack with 23 brand new skins to select from!\r\n\r\nCreator's Note: This pack was mostly made for fun (partially jokingly) back in 2021. I had not previously published it before, but now it is free to use in Bedrock Cosmos!
